@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zokrfs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.33
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.22 - v0 + 0.07) * (v1 + 0.04 + v0 + 0.61)) / v2)
    v0 = v0
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.74 + v2 + 0.12)))
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (0.60 - wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.97)))
    data[tid] = v0
